name: Verde Traders
overview:
Our store offers new and used furniture, vintage and collectible items. Visit our shop and you may have that exclusive antique you’re searching for.

Verde Investors is a exceptional Antique store. At Verde Traders, we are consistently have new and interesting items that come in and out of our shop. With competitive and variable costs new products never last long.. Like us on Facebook and see new items we have in our store and get special offers and coupons!
